com.hms_networks.americas.sc.azure.data

Class AZConnectorPayloadArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hms_networks.americas.sc.azure.data.AZConnectorPayload
      • com.hms_networks.americas.sc.azure.data.AZConnectorPayloadArray

  • public class AZConnectorPayloadArray
extends AZConnectorPayload
    Azure payload class that adds each payload to a JSON array called datapoints and has no added constraints. This payload is not able to be decoded in Microsoft PowerBI.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    HMS Networks, MU Americas Solution Center
